N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 18 ยง 351.10 - Identification and referral of adolescents to case management activities

State Regulations
A pregnant or parenting adolescent who is receiving
public assistance or is a payee of such benefits on behalf of his or her
child(ren) must be identified and referred to the appropriate unit or agency
for case management activities as described in Part 361 of this
